
	php:
	====

		- hyper text preprocessor.

		- use: to crete web page application.

		- server side scripting langauge.

		- server side (it is used to connect more database).

		- open source software (no license)

		- developed by :  rasmus lerdrof.

		- extension: .php
		
		- joining operator: .
		
    		-php is a interpreter. (line by line error check. show only one error)
		- php case sensitive language.
    
    - php is a front end tool (manipulation work)
    
    - php is also supported oops
    
    - back end tool "mysql" inbuilt.   

		- software:
			xampp,wamp,lamp.

		-code: any text editor
			notepad,sublimetext,.....

		-output:
			any web browser

			- IE,Google chrome,......
		
		procedure: (how to run simple php program)
		==========================================

		step 1:	xampp control panel open.
		step 2: apache start.
		step 3: open notepad or sublime
		step 4: write simple program.
			<?php
				echo "welcome to php";
			?>
		step 5: save only: c:/xampp/htdocs/yourfolder/filename.php

		step 6:open browser :
			address bar(type):http://localhost/yourfolder/filename.php
